Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:37.49,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,38.3 degrees...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:39.85,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone down a bit since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:42.06,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,You need to stay in bed all day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:46.00,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Hona, where's Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:49.63,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,She came back from her night shift \Nand went out to do some shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:52.38,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:53.75,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,A delivery?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:55.74,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:00.32,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:00.97,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:03.49,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. We're here to pay \NUmika-chan a visit—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:06.25,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is Umika all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.99,0:02:08.02,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Pogyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:10.69,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I don't know who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:13.72,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,but if you're here to pick on Onee-chan, \Ncome back when she feels better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:14.28,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:17.15,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,What, do we look like bullies to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:19.16,DefaultItalics,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,You're the spitting image of one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:21.48,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for visiting without any notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.29,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Umika-chan collapsed during \Nour club activities yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:32.42,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(777,1)\fs12\fnTimes New Roman\c&H424152&\pos(228,206)\blur2\t(26,777,\blur0.1)}Alien
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:28.87,Flashback,Umika's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,I got a phone call from Umika's clubmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:31.00,Flashback,Umika's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,They brought her to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.60,Flashback,Umika's Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness she was with her friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:35.17,DefaultItalics,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.72,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Um, my mother told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:40.63,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:43.14,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,I must have surprised you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.59,0:02:46.83,DefaultItalics,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan really {\i0}did{\i1} have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:49.26,DefaultItalics,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she's a big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:53.27,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.63,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends from club are here to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:58.76,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:02:59.46,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:02.24,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize you weren't feeling well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:05.16,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a useless alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:06.00,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:08.04,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Take nice, deep breaths of my space energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:10.79,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.54,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Huff, huff, supiiv!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:14.29,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Huff, huff, supiiv!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:24.30,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\bord2.5\fnComic Sans MS\c&HFDFDF9&\3c&H2F228E&}Convinced
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:18.47,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,She really {\i1}is{\i0} Onee-chan's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:19.36,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Vuvuvuv...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:21.34,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,We are tomoraav!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:22.66,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Stop playing along!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:24.30,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,She's gonna think {\i1}I'm{\i0} like that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:28.31,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:30.78,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently it was complications from a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:33.46,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,She should get better with some good rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:34.55,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:35.62,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:39.07,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,We got you plenty of yummy gelatin snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:40.92,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,So feel free to eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:44.02,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:46.58,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for pushing you too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:47.73,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Nuh-uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:51.33,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's... launch rockets again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:54.58,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.13,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, so rest up and feel better!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:01.02,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking beet red as well, Matataki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:02.23,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:03.22,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:05.54,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make sure you don't have a fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:05.72,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(483,392)\fs40\fnArial Black\c&HB469F7&\bord1\shad2\3c&H524B54&\4c&H524B54&\frz29.17\move(183,89.5,151,25,24,2443)}F{\c&HF0748E&}o{\c&HB469F7&}r{\c&HF0748E&}e{\c&HB469F7&}h{\c&HF0748E&}e{\c&HB469F7&}a{\c&HF0748E&}d{\c&HB469F7&}p{\c&HF0748E&}a{\c&HB469F7&}t{\c&HF0748E&}h{\c&HB469F7&}y
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:06.88,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:07.97,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.38,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to fight, take it outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.38,DefaultTop,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! I'll check for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:11.98,DefaultTop,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I said there's no need!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:12.85,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can eat some congee?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.95,DefaultTop,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Matataki's a grumpy little alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:14.93,DefaultTop,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your face, bun nut!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:17.86,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Her forehead... I bet it's nice and cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:21.80,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Why am {\i1}I{\i0} helping out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:23.36,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Me next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:26.41,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to swarm in here out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:27.62,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.60,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.80,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:33.20,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Are your parents at work today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:34.12,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:37.46,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my mother came home earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:40.13,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,but she went out right away to go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:44.78,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,She works at an aquarium, so she \Nhas to take night duty sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:50.88,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why I was looking \Nafter Onee-chan last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:52.54,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:53.14,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(613,1)\an6\fs26\fnComic Sans MS\c&H95928F&\3c&H625C56&\4c&H665D50&\bord1\shad2\frz10.8\pos(613,53)}Slight sense of guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.62,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,She's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:58.72,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:00.77,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,She fell asleep while standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:02.94,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,A far cry from her clumsy big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:02.94,DefaultTop,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:03.99,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:07.67,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,She can stay asleep in my arms like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:11.29,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,No, you go and change our chairwoman's \Nforehead-cooling pad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:17.79,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,All right, guess I'll have to \Nlook after her on the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.18,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:21.05,DefaultTop,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Matataki-chan, you help me with the cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:44.32,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,My forehead feels so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:48.82,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Akeuchi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.26,DefaultTop,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Pathy, pathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.44,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Harunopathy! Matatakipathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:55.25,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Harunopathy! Matatakipathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.83,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Akeuchi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:06:01.09,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What about my forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:02.22,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:05.59,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say before that you \Ndidn't want foreheadpathy from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:08.59,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the one person \Nwho's not getting any!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.15,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I think Haruno will get it all for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:15.36,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now. Don't leave me out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.06,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Just Matataki, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.85,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:25.61,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:27.68,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That fever seems intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:30.86,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you pushed \Nyourself a bit too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:36.41,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, everyone was able \Nto stand next to each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:39.37,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's just like I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:45.75,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You've done a fine job as our chairwoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:50.13,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, did I wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:52.26,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.50,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:57.50,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Haruno and Matataki are making congee...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.53,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.28,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Did you change the pad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.28,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,How's Umika-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:14.55,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:16.29,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking a bit flushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:17.79,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel feverish?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.83,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the big deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:24.96,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:29.72,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I want your foreheadpathy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:31.75,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:33.59,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.65,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Let me be the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.94,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,My forehead... My forehead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.36,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all sold out for the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.81,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. None of us are buying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:53.76,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,When are you getting in your next batch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:54.58,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Next batch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:55.99,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Next batch... Next batch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.29,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.24,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,My forehead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:01.05,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:09.21,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:11.06,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,With guests over and everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:15.79,Default,Honami,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:31.15,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.11,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats on your recovery, Umi-chairwoman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:36.86,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry for making you all worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.83,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you got over your cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.84,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Now for Matataki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:42.62,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on coming back to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.91,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it out loud like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:46.33,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,It only makes it awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:47.72,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Raimon-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.12,0:08:50.04,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I really am so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:52.59,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,That look also makes me \Nuncomfortable, so cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:53.83,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:57.05,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei was giving me the \Ncreeps the whole day, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.51,Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Raimon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.56,Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You know you can't do \Nother stuff during class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:05.13,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Emihara-sensei was worried \Nabout you the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:06.44,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of her business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.82,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You say that, but how do you {\i1}really{\i0} feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:10.74,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly the same, word for word!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.90,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Stop always trying to bump foreheads!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:18.94,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,That smarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:20.88,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let go all of a sudden like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:22.41,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:27.00,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan, you've been a little \Nout of it ever since our visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:27.46,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.42,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did you catch my cold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:31.21,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.67,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.52,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,But, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:38.98,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,My forehead is burning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:39.86,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,That's a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:41.05,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:43.06,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:47.78,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Moving on, looks like the Rocket Research \NHobby Group is back in business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.28,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,You're changing the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:51.68,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umi-chairwoman, tell us \Nyour plan for the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:52.90,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:57.15,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:10:00.03,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:03.21,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that energy from before go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.20,FlashbackItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make it to space together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:07.04,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(484,1)\fs32\fnArial Black\bord0.5\shad1\pos(466,29)}Bold
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:10.24,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,W-We have so many goals,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:12.79,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(565,1)\fnArial Black\c&H659BB8&\3c&H08030A&\4c&H08030A&\bord0.8\shad1.5\frz6.047\pos(120.5,7.5)}Outer space
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:12.79,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(565,1)\fnArial Black\c&H659BB8&\3c&H08030A&\4c&H08030A&\bord0.8\shad1.5\frz6.047\pos(291.5,66.5)}Manned rocket
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:12.79,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(565,1)\fnArial Black\c&H659BB8&\3c&H08030A&\4c&H08030A&\bord0.8\shad1.5\frz6.047\pos(293.5,150)}Championship
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:12.79,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(565,1)\fnArial Black\c&H659BB8&\3c&H08030A&\4c&H08030A&\bord0.8\shad1.5\frz6.047\pos(515.5,15.5)}Hobby group
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:12.79,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(565,1)\fnArial Black\c&H659BB8&\3c&H08030A&\4c&H08030A&\bord0.8\shad1.5\frz6.047\pos(558.5,170.5)}Model\Nrocket
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:12.79,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,s-so I gave it lots of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:17.55,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,F-For now, I-I was thinking of \Nentering next year's championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.77,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We have a year until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:25.91,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,T-To that end, we f-first need the \Nschool to recognize our activities
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:29.81,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,a-and promote us to a full-fledged club, \Ni-in my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:32.09,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-If we stay a hobby group,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:35.08,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,i-it'll be really hard getting permission \Nfor a launch spot, like last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:36.82,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1482,476)\fs16\bord2\fnComic Sans MS\c&H111D36&\3c&H96B0CE&\frz15.79\pos(470,53.5)}Scary\Nteacher
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.29,Default,Teacher A,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it dangerous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:41.32,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like we can use this basement \Nfor all the steps of our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:41.07,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(567,556)\fs30\fnComic Sans MS\c&H1E1A18&\3c&HECECEA&\bord2\shad1\4a&H66&\pos(169.5,23.5)}Cramped!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:42.96,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,And we need money, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:44.08,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(738,1)\fs30\fnComic Sans MS\c&H1E1A18&\3c&HECECEA&\bord2\shad1\4a&H66&\frz12.68\pos(400.5,98)}Rocket parts
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:44.08,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(780,1)\fs20\fnComic Sans MS\c&H1E1A18&\3c&HECECEA&\bord2\shad1\4a&H66&\frz13.15\pos(126,75)}Simulation software
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.86,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:49.81,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we launch rockets at school \Nto show off to all the teachers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:54.09,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(609,1)\fnComic Sans MS\c&HB30227&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\frz345.1\pos(323.5,107.5)}Surprise\N{\c&HEA0074&}kaboom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:50.97,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:52.08,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Memo, memo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:54.09,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to get us disbanded?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.91,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at past examples,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:11:00.15,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,the Adventive Plant Research Society won \Nan award at a science research competition
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:05.10,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1025,1)\fs15\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\c&H120835&\3c&HFDFEFC&\pos(250.5,165.5)}Award
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:02.63,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,and were promoted to a full-fledged club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:04.10,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Adventive?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:05.10,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Memo, memo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.14,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:09.38,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go depending on results \Nthat we may never get.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:10.49,DefaultItalics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:14.82,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,We should spend our own money on model \Nrockets and put them to good use instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:15.88,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Memo, memo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:20.24,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,We'll unleash our fury on \Nsmall local tournaments!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.24,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Fury?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:22.71,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:25.03,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I've looked into past records.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:29.41,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,The top prizes will be a piece of cake, \Neven if we reuse the same rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:31.87,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,It's the fastest path to getting \Nour club promoted!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.07,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,And where to from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:37.07,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take down those Tatsuoka \Njerks at the championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:38.85,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,So that's your real goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:39.63,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:42.84,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,B-Build up accomplishments \Nat smaller tournaments,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:45.13,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,and beat Akizuki-san at \Nthe national tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:46.39,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.69,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to write all that down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:51.36,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,That's just my personal goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:54.11,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to make it \Nthe whole group's goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:55.06,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:12:00.44,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give meaning to the things \NI make with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:05.23,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Making a rocket that doesn't fly the way \NI want and leaves no mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:06.45,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:10.90,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll try again \Nat next year's championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:15.21,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,For my own personal goal, \NI'll be a part of this group.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:19.20,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,So, Chairwoman, be honest \Nwith yourself about your goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:21.14,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,and think about what you \Nwant to do from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:25.22,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold back like you did before, \Nonly to break down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:28.51,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,My goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:34.52,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I want to g-get better \Nat speaking to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:39.78,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've been thinking back on my speech at the \Nchampionship th-this whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:44.53,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,w-wondering how I could \Nhave done a better job speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:50.87,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't get better, i-it'll only cause \Nmore problems down the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:54.87,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't want to keep ignoring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:59.65,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become a p-proper leader, \Nand that's one part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:03.38,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,That's my goal right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:08.18,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I know I said to be \Nhonest about your goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.57,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,but communication skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:13.64,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry it's not something \Nmore aligned with the group!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:15.39,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:22.65,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You see, to be honest, I haven't yet come up \Nwith a goal like the ones you all have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:27.08,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I know Umika-chan and Matataki-chan \Nhave their own dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:31.91,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,And Yu-chan has the big goal of \Nreturning to her home planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:35.88,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,But I still don't have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:40.30,Flashback,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You said I didn't have \Nanything that I really loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:45.55,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, all I did was repeat \Nthings I'd heard elsewhere, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:50.80,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,So if there's anything I can do, \NI want to give it my all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:56.44,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,And it'd be nice if I could find something \Nto call my own in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:57.17,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:00.06,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let's put together everyone's thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:02.15,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,601)\blur0.2\fnComic Sans MS\c&H1A1C47&\pos(326,233.5)}Rocket Notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:03.57,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,and come up with a new plan \Nfor our future activities!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:08.20,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Steadily, at our own pace, \None step at a time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:12.28,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,We'll work toward a rocket \Nto reach the stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:21.21,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:23.46,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Time to try my best today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:27.73,Default,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,Konohoshi-san, bona-morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:30.38,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ah, morn-avuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:31.37,Default,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:39.78,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,S-Struck with wonder, he did approach, \No-o-only to find the bamboo stalk aglow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:44.56,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-Turning his gaze within, there rested a \Nl-lovely babe but three sun in l-l-length!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:46.80,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Konohoshi-san, take a breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:47.94,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:53.53,DefaultItalics,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika's trying her best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:01.93,DefaultItalics,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,The winner of the national Model Rocket \NChampionship, two years in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:04.54,DefaultItalics,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuoka High School of \NScience and Technology!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:08.54,DefaultItalics,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Flaunting the might of the reigning \Nchamp with a stable launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:10.31,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,National champions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:11.55,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,That's so awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:14.99,Default,Kaneda,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuoka... Isn't that the STEM school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.06,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.06,DefaultTop,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:20.27,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Konohoshi-san's team duked it out \Nwith them for points in the qualifiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.19,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Hiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:23.72,Default,Kaneda,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Konohoshi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:27.16,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're not the amazing ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:28.69,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,All we did was lose to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:31.95,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I watched the stream \Nof the finals yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:36.27,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,a-and I sent Akizuki-san my congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:38.80,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,This is the trophy they got!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:39.61,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.32,0:15:43.53,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,For next year, we'll need to get stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:45.71,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,so we can compete alongside them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:46.60,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:52.22,Default,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:54.19,Default,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,What're you all watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.47,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Nasshi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:56.94,Default,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Here, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:15:59.05,Default,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,It's a video of a model rocket launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:00.31,Default,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:02.60,Default,Kaneda,0000,0000,0000,,They fly using gunpowder engines!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:04.30,Default,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:05.61,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Kinashi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:08.33,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,She always strikes up conversations with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:11.90,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,but because I'm so hopeless, \NI've never really talked with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:15.19,Default,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,That looks way bland!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:16.63,Default,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.37,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(360,1)\fnArial Black\c&HFDFEF8&\pos(325.5,38)}Bland
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.12,Default,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.58,Default,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,It's not bland at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:22.11,Default,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Konohoshi-san and her \Nfriends build them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:23.01,Default,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:24.06,Default,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:25.90,Default,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always run your mouth like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:27.16,Default,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:30.76,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,1)\bord0.8\shad0.5\4a&H66&\fnArial Black\c&H14FFED&\3c&H1F1F1F&\4c&H1F1F1F&\frz5.023\pos(92,20.5)}Nas-shy with\N{\c&H49FFAD&}her words
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.56,DefaultItalics,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it {\i0}is{\i1} a bit bland.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:30.76,DefaultItalics,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,That's the good part.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:33.13,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Model rockets are the latest hot thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:34.92,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Konohoshi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:39.39,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Now's your chance to show off what you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:44.75,Flashback,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I want to g-get better at speaking to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.42,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kinashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:53.20,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess model rockets...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:58.24,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,m-might be a little b-boring \Nor bland to set up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:04.25,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,b-but when they fly at i-incredible speeds \Non launch, they're really cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:02.80,DefaultItalicsTop,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,Konohoshi-san called me by my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.89,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I brought one with me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:08.92,Default,Group,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.00,Default,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, but why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:15.70,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:19.89,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I th-think Kinashi-san hates me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:24.65,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,You sounded like a real freak \Nblabbing on back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.70,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Bad Matataki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:27.85,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:30.15,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Nasshi was listening to you really seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:32.04,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:33.60,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:38.30,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,While I was talking, Kinashi-san \Nwent silent halfway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:40.71,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she totally tuned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:42.16,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Bad Matataki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:46.19,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Nasshi-chan said she'd watch the video later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:48.92,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and you became texting friends, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:53.63,Flashback,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,Send me the link to the video!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:56.17,Flashback,Kinachi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, do we have each other added?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:18:02.14,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She laughed at how long it took, \Nc-considering I sit right behind her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:04.60,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm glad I got to add her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.23,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay! I'm good now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:10.01,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk about our club!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:12.32,DefaultItalics,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit, Umika!
