Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:17.45,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,143)\bord2\b0\fs14\an7\blur0.2\frz28.94\fax0.23\c&H38345A&\3c&HF2F6FA&\pos(275,313)}Konohoshi-san, good luck with your club~
