Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.46,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can't let her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.44,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,H-How should I reply?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:31.59,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Should we send a photo in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:32.21,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Pho—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:34.45,DefaultTop,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't point the camera this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:33.96,DefaultItalics,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:36.09,DefaultItalics,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,She looks so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:44.60,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it's already dark out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.35,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,The days are getting shorter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:49.25,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:50.03,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:52.61,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,S-See you later, Akeuchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.50,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:04.50,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I left something behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:07.41,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,F-F-Feel free to go on without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:16.33,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Umika-chan's really become a lot stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:17.67,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:20.42,Flashback,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I want to find \Na place where I belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:21.46,FlashbackTop,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Those goggles! They're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:22.63,FlashbackTop,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:25.37,Flashback,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think I managed to speak \Nclearly until the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:27.52,FlashbackTop,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I-I'm sorry... I can't do it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:29.43,Flashback,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's aim for the skies together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:33.59,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,She's always been strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:48.33,DefaultItalics,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,My forehead feels so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:50.83,DefaultItalics,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:53.88,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Found you, Akeuchi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:55.88,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:57.59,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:20:01.76,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Um, have you not been feeling \Nwell this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:04.51,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm feeling totally fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:07.83,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the space energy has become unstable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.63,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:13.27,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,If you need anything, I can go and get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:14.56,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:16.77,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm totally a-okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:18.07,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:21.78,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your forehead feels cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:26.24,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,But y-you've always been \Non the cooler side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.32,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akeuchi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:30.04,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:32.00,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:33.96,Flashback,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Your foreheadpathy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.49,0:20:37.26,Flashback,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Let me be the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:40.34,DefaultItalics,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's Umika's fault for saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:48.70,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I haven't done foreheadpathy \Nwith anyone today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:49.25,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:50.01,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.27,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:55.52,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:58.77,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi...san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:02.12,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Your face... is red.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:08.74,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you feeling sick after all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:10.74,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! I'm fine! I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:12.21,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:18.34,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akeuchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:21.13,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let me see your forehead for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:23.13,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.58,0:21:25.86,DefaultItalics,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:29.29,DefaultItalics,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,She's so, so worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:32.21,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:37.22,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.95,0:21:41.95,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,All of your feelings reached me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:43.90,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.09,0:21:45.23,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:47.26,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:55.16,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you've always been \Nso sincere with your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:21:57.95,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Shining so brightly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:22:00.17,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,and full of warmth...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.00,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:07.77,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,When you first introduced \Nyourself to me, I was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.64,0:22:13.00,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,When you told me your lifelong dream \Nwas to build a rocket to go to outer space
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:16.18,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,and find aliens to be your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.91,0:22:19.88,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Alien friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.96,0:22:23.69,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:28.45,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go to outer space in the \Nrocket we all build together!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:30.74,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,That's my dream now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.81,0:22:32.68,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:36.00,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.22,0:22:39.00,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything, Akeuchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.28,0:22:41.83,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll give it all I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:45.86,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I may not be very reliable yet,
